name: Step It Up! Step It Up! Step It Up! Step It Up!
description:
Step It Up! Step It Up! Step It Up! Step It Up! is a mixed media collage in motion. The story behind the artwork is simple and clear. You need to step it up. Every single moment. Never settle for less. Reach to the sky and beyond. There is no limit. 

MPEG-4 / 1080 × 1080 / Duration 00:04

May the consciousness of this artwork guide you in moments of doubt and help you to become better version of yourself.  

Step It Up! Step It Up! Step It Up! Step It Up! By Christian Roman

Christian Roman is a photographer & digital artist based in London.
